text: Very cosy ambiance with very good food! Super cosy double storey bistro. Beautiful and friendly waitresses.

The food is disgusting, they take too long, they forgot a lot of what we ordered, we waited for almost 2 hours to eat slop on a plate, I wouldn't even feed this to my dog. Horrendous. The seating as well is beyond messed up, unclean. This place looks like a health hazard. Please never come here.

1 for 1 lunch deal for the western food extremely worthwhile, cheaper and better tasting than the western food at the hawker center, approximately $6.45 split 2 ways. Food is excellent, chicken chop not overcooked and well marinated/spiced, however the mushroom soup leaves much to be desired.
The food did not taste good. It took one hour to receive the food. They forgot the order. Sofa is not clean.

Great service with good food
Nice place for group gathering
Boss there also very friendly
